      <content><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>Open the <a title="Demo application" href="%(link0)" target="_blank" rel="noopener">demo application</a>.</li>
<li>See how the page looks like in the <a title="Editable web view" href="%(link1)" target="_blank" rel="noopener">editable web view</a> (requires login).</li>
<li>The view shows one and the same content in many different display variations (image left, image right, only image, etc.).</li>
<li>From the web view, open the element settings editor.</li>
<li>Play with the different settings, click save, and see how the changes are reflected in the demo application.</li>
</ul>]]></content>
